name: sum rap songs
description:
an album by Earl Sweatshirt that was able to change my vision about how we deal with our feelings and our creations. In my conception, Some Rap Songs is an album made by simplifying earl ideas and evading unsimplified fractions 'cause this is stressful sometimes. It's about how simple and easy is to love what we create and deal with our feelings about that thing.

This is a tribute. 

Made on Photoshop, 2019
